channel.title: YTV subliminal messaging
channel.description:
I was watching YTV (top kids televison channel in canada) now, i like one show called mystery hunters and have liked it for a long time. It shows at 11 p.m EST.
Now before that, some boring shit called Falcon Beach was finishing up. Around 10:54-11:00 p.m YTV was advertising a show, and right after I saw a black flash and I was like WTF? I could only catch a glimpse of it because it was like 1/10 of a second long. Anyways all i remember was seeing a date, on the message.

edit: I saw it twice, this time i saw the same date and the word 'fetch'
